# Ajouter serveur Hyper-V distant

### PowerShell admin 

```
$Server = "ERIS1-HYPERV" 
$IP = "172.16.199.101" 
$User   = "Server\Administrateur" 

winrm quickconfig 
Set-Item WSMan:\localhost\Client\TrustedHosts -Value "$Server,$IP" -Force 
Restart-Service WinRM 
cmdkey /add:ERIS1-HYPERV /user:ERIS1-HYPERV\Administrateur /pass:Console@19 
cmdkey /add:172.16.199.101 /user:ERIS1-HYPERV\Administrateur /pass:Console@19 

Test-WSMan $Server 
```
